 next to Orchestra (the picture definitely isn&#039;t rule 63 Big Mac), and he leans a bit toward him. &quot;Why hello there! It looked as if you were alone...so I came to keep you company.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402052426";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#2bb7b3";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020380221";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c41818";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664602;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664602";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:4:"text";s:63:"(It&#039;s not. Different hair, style, hooves, and Cutie Mark.)";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402052533";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020381314";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664603;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664603";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10669";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"806";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:15:"(Hmm...touche.)";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402052618";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#2bb7b3";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020382143";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c41818";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664604;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664604";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:4:"text";s:293:"/me gave him a smirk. &quot;Oh really now?&quot; He said with a quick chuckle. A very neutral sounding voice. &quot;I am fine in the company of myself. Are you sure you didn&#039;t sit with me because you are the lonely one?~&quot; He teased a bit, then raised his violin to continue his song.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402052636";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020382344";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664607;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664607";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10669";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"806";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:184:"/me shrugs. &quot;Well, I could be the lonely one..well, I am..but eh........&quot; he gives a long pause, then clears his throat. &quot;I&#039;m Star, Frozen Star...just call me Star.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402052779";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#2bb7b3";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020383747";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c41818";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664608;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664608";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10669";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"806";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:11:" (assbutts)";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402052787";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#2bb7b3";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020383825";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c41818";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664609;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664609";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10669";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"806";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:279:"/me shrugs. &quot;Well, I could be the lonely one..well, I am..but eh........&quot; he gives a long pause, then clears his throat. &quot;I&#039;m Star, Frozen Star...just call me Star.&quot; he rubs the back of his neck and sits back awkwardly. &quot;What&#039;s your name?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402052814";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#2bb7b3";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020384099";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c41818";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664611;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664611";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:4:"text";s:50:"https://derpicdn.net/img/2013/4/23/306020/full.png";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402052851";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020384499";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664615;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664615";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10669";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"806";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:6:"(heh.)";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402052978";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#2bb7b3";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020385739";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c41818";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664616;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664616";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:4:"text";s:411:"/me looked over at him with a smile. &quot;Heh... cute.&quot; He said, looking up and down the nicely built and toned stallion. Not half bad for his likings. Stopping his play of the violin, he sat it down. &quot;My name is Ludwig Von Bach Strings. Most just call me Orchestra. Germane names are understandably hard to grasp.&quot; He said, then giggled. &quot;Guess you are just looking for company, huh?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402052984";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020385829";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664620;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664620";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10669";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"806";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:290:"/me pricks up his ears and brushes the mane out of his face. &quot;Uuuuh, well, not exactly, but It&#039;d be nice to....well....yes.&quot; he clears his throat. &quot;And...to be honest, sir, I thought you were a woman, and to be honest...I&#039;m not very disappointed.&quot; he chuckles.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402053201";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#2bb7b3";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020387965";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c41818";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664624;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664624";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:4:"text";s:377:"/me smiled. &quot;It&#039;s fine. Most others assume I am a cute little mare anyhow. It doesn&#039;t really effect me.&quot; Orchestra had a mischeaveous and turned on expression in his eyes, imagining this perfect stallion in bed. Having not done anything in quite awhile left him in a sexually open state. &quot;Well Star. Got a place for us to go?&quot; He leaned in closer.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402053440";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020390387";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:664630;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"664630";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10669";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Frozen_Star";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"806";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:321:"/me gulps. He had no escape, not like he really wanted to either. He could even feel the pressure rising in his loins. &quot;Erm. Well, I do have my house, it isn&#039;t too far away, and it&#039;s got a pretty big bed...&quot; he then quickly stands up and aids Orchestra to his hooves, heading quickly toward his house.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1402053559";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#2bb7b3";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14020391551";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c41818";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i: